{"tid":619330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"食環票控回收店爆衝突 南亞街坊圍觀幫手遭㩒地","createTime":"2018-04-06T14:05:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-07T05:33:45.000Z","uid":28765,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2b0ec6ebcddf80c5cfb7c59707f5e1e76c488a38","tid":619330,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T14:05:28.000Z","msg":"食環署職員與市民爆發生衝突，下午4時許，數名食環署員於大南街259號對開巡邏，其間發現一間回收店門外擺放一批首飾，上前打算票控非法擺賣，南亞店東與兒子與食環職員理論，雙方發生爭執，附近的南亞街坊見狀上前圍觀起哄，食環職員見狀報警求助。據街坊提供的片段所見，現場情況混亂，其中一名南亞男子遭食環署員按在地上。<br />\n<br />\n警方衝鋒車接報趕至，將人群分隔，涉事南亞父子、南亞街坊及5名食環署職員均報稱受傷，須召救護車送院檢查。警方正就事件展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180406/58042289\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180406%2F58042289&d=v%2FFFyb0r89fiJAo8Co9bFtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=34b602ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180406%2F58042289&h=d49aac75\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180406/58042289</a><br />\n<br />\n食環今次咁勇武既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b4b75053e13a8e4ae0fe2313e68e96f37540f7a","tid":619330,"uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T14:19:12.000Z","msg":"平時食環遇到老人會瞓低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n阿伯&gt;食環&gt;南亞"},{"pid":"fd217f9f2efc0cdbd0e27f5488af4de7f6d69304","tid":619330,"uid":50328,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T14:25:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7ea0e44a7e7dd311f4b68b6ae6927a3ac94d13c1","tid":619330,"uid":53705,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T14:31:31.000Z","msg":"如果食環 專門搞 南亞人, 唔去搞阿伯<br />\n相信都唔會咁多憎 食環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n市民憎食環, 主要唔係憎佢地執法, 而係憎佢地欺善怕惡, 專門搞阿伯阿婆, 